-- CADP (CONSTRUCTION AND ANALYSIS OF DISTRIBUTED PROCESSES)
-- http://cadp.inria.fr

This directory contains the following files:

 - bes.xml:         Notepad++ syntax mode for the BES format
 - exp.xml:         Notepad++ syntax mode for the EXP format
 - lnt.xml:         Notepad++ syntax mode for the LNT language
 - lotos.xml:       Notepad++ syntax mode for the LOTOS language
 - mcl.xml:         Notepad++ syntax mode for the MCL language
 - nupn.xml:        Notepad++ syntax mode for the NUPN format
 - rbc.xml:         Notepad++ syntax mode for the RBC format
 - svl.xml:         Notepad++ syntax mode for the SVL language
 - xtl.xml:         Notepad++ syntax mode for the XTL language

How to use these files:
-----------------------

Follow the explanations given in Section 3 ("How to install user defined
language file") of the following document:

http://docs.notepad-plus-plus.org/index.php?title=User_Defined_Language_Files


